snippet.title: Test Drive Unlimited Solar Crown - Welcome to Hong Kong Island
snippet.description:
The next step in your Solar Crown adventure starts today. Kylotonn Studios and Nacon Publishing are proud to present the location of Test Drive Unlimited Solar crown as Hong Kong Island!

Navigate the bustling island in glorious 1:1 scale, and be absorbed by the city. Pick your path as either STREETS or SHARPS and let your personality shine.
